            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* $9,000,000,000 for NASA's Science Mission Directorate (SMD) to maintain U.S. leadership in space exploration and scientific discovery.\n* Supports high-priority decadal survey missions and protects the specialized aerospace workforce from further instability.\n* Ensures the U.S. remains the partner of choice for international missions and stays competitive with China's expanding space science program.\n* Provides essential data for weather forecasting, planetary defense, and national security through advanced satellite and sensor technology.",
